        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[FromSoftware has finally announced an Elden Ring Switch 2 release date]]></title>
            <link>https://www.eurogamer.net/elden-ring-switch-2-release-date</link>
            <guid>1539388</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>
      <article data-ads="true" data-article-type="news" data-article-group="news" data-paywalled="false" data-premium="false" data-sponsored="false" data-type="article">


<header data-component="article-header">
  

    


  <p>

  <figure>
      <picture>
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Elden-Ring-knight-with-a-sword-over-thier-shoulder-and-a-Switch-2-logo-in-the-upper-left-corner.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 1dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Elden-Ring-knight-with-a-sword-over-thier-shoulder-and-a-Switch-2-logo-in-the-upper-left-corner.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.5&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 1.5dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Elden-Ring-knight-with-a-sword-over-thier-shoulder-and-a-Switch-2-logo-in-the-upper-left-corner.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.75&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 1.75dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Elden-Ring-knight-with-a-sword-over-thier-shoulder-and-a-Switch-2-logo-in-the-upper-left-corner.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=2&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 2dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Elden-Ring-knight-with-a-sword-over-thier-shoulder-and-a-Switch-2-logo-in-the-upper-left-corner.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=3&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 3dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Elden-Ring-knight-with-a-sword-over-thier-shoulder-and-a-Switch-2-logo-in-the-upper-left-corner.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;auto=webp" media="(min-width: 550px) and (max-resolution: 1dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Elden-Ring-knight-with-a-sword-over-thier-shoulder-and-a-Switch-2-logo-in-the-upper-left-corner.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.5&amp;auto=webp" media="(min-width: 550px) and (max-resolution: 1.5dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Elden-Ring-knight-with-a-sword-over-thier-shoulder-and-a-Switch-2-logo-in-the-upper-left-corner.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.75&amp;auto=webp" media="(min-width: 550px) and (max-resolution: 1.75dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Elden-Ring-knight-with-a-sword-over-thier-shoulder-and-a-Switch-2-logo-in-the-upper-left-corner.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=2&amp;auto=webp" media="(min-width: 550px) and (max-resolution: 2dppx)">
        
      </picture>

        <figcaption>
          <span>Image credit: <cite>Eurogamer</cite></span>
        </figcaption>
  </figure>
  </p>

    

</header>
  <div data-component="article-content">


            <p>FromSoftware and <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/companies/bandai-namco-entertainment">Bandai Namco Entertainment</a> have finally announced a <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/platforms/switch-2">Switch 2</a> release date for <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/elden-ring-walkthrough-8042">Elden Ring</a>.</p>
<p>Elden Ring will be released on Switch 2 on 28th August, packaged as the Tarnished Edition. This includes the base game as well as Elden Ring's Shadow of the Erdtree expansion.</p>

<figure>
<p>
<a aria-label="Elden Ring: Tarnished Edition - Official Nintendo Switch 2 Trailer" data-platform="youtube" href="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pMeYxev9PZM?autoplay=1" onclick="((e) => { e.preventDefault(); e.currentTarget.closest('.video_wrapper').innerHTML = e.currentTarget.querySelector('template').innerHTML; enableElements(); })(event)" title="Click to play video from YouTube">
<span>Elden Ring: Tarnished Edition - Official Nintendo Switch 2 Trailer</span>
<template>
<iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pMeYxev9PZM?autoplay=1" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/pMeYxev9PZM?autoplay=1" title="Elden Ring: Tarnished Edition - Official Nintendo Switch 2 Trailer">
</iframe> </template>
</a>
</p>
<figcaption>Elden Ring Switch 2 trailer. <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pMeYxev9PZM" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Watch on YouTube</a></figcaption></figure>


<p>In addition, <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/elden-ring-tarnished-edition-to-include-two-new-classes">Elden Ring: Tarnished Edition will come with</a> two new starting classes, all-new character armour and customisation options for Torrent. These new things are also being made  available to buy on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, and PC.</p><p>Elden Ring was first released back in 2022, and quickly <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/elden-ring-sales-pass-30m">became a huge  success for developer FromSoftware</a>. Its <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-tips-and-tricks">Shadow of the Erdtree DLC followed</a>, as did <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/elden-ring-nightreign-tips-tricks">multiplayer spin-off Nightreign</a>. Elden Ring  was <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/elden-ring-is-coming-to-switch-2">meant to make its Switch 2 debut last year</a>, however its <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/switch-2-elden-ring-tarnished-edition-delayed-to-2026-to-allow-time-for-performance-adjustments">release was delayed to "allow time for performance adjustments"</a>.</p>
<p>If you've not played Elden Ring yet and are thinking about picking it up on Switch 2, be sure to check out <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/elden-ring-review">Eurogamer's original Elden Ring review from 2022</a>, where Aoife Wilson called it "grandiose", "mysterious" and "a touch more welcoming" than FromSoftware's previous games.</p>
<figure>
 


<figcaption><span>Image credit: <cite>FromSoft</cite></span></figcaption>
</figure>
<p>Elsewhere in news from the Lands Between, the Elden Ring movie adaptation is underway and set to arrive in theatres on 3rd March, 2028. Earlier this year, the <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/elden-ring-movie-cast-announced">cast for the Elden Ring film was announced</a>, with Alien: Romulus and Wake Up Dead Man: A Knives Out Mystery actress Cailee Spaeny in a lead role. Other confirmed cast members include Ben Whishaw, Kit Connor, Peter Serafinowicz and Nick Offerman, to name a few. Allegedly, the <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/elden-ring-film-budget-a24s-largest-and-most-ambitious-project-yet">upcoming film from Alex Garland and production company A24 has a budget "well over" $100m</a>.</p>

        </div>

  
      </article>






